        {
            "title": "立足股壇｜港股今輪調整未完 本月仍有下行機會｜JK爸爸（陳立展）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0vyqIEp_FgisvJnkkSnMbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bossmind_356/b8787da02bb3f5c7f5fa5b9a531a0e1d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股在4月最後一個交易日再次失守兩萬六，今輪的調整料未完成，5月仍偏向有進一步下行風險的較高，跌穿25,000點的機會高於50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按最新的資金盤路來看，部署5月期權的資金不多，故5月初出現單邊走勢的機會不大。惟由於資金未有改變從4月高位開始看淡的部署，故預期恒指在5月尚有下跌空間，但最終會大跌或小跌，則仍需進一步觀察，策略上要保持靈活性，進攻性淡倉在跌至25,200點至25,400點時可先獲利，但防守性淡倉需繼續持有。若五一長假期後資金部署有進一步轉弱情況，5月的低位或會較4月低位更低。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b40cf12e-6fff-327d-849c-4104b996eda2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利是股奇瑞汽車（9973）在4月上旬升至33元時，當時已提醒不應高追，現時確實回落至28.82元。然而，該股跌至現水平可開始逐步吸納。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊（700）跌至467.8元，短期走勢雖長，但中長期部署則應吸納，可考慮行使價450元的沽出認沽期權（Short Put)。至於阿里（9988）方面，在125元可買入第一注，之後在120元及110元再分段部署。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>陳立展（JK爸爸</strong>）<br/><strong>獨立股評人<br/>資深期權投資者</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"img\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/jksir_seminar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zJUKb6euOycbcikgLKX_Mw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bossmind_356/02558232bd3a1f5108de0237d78fb483\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
